      ## Install
  .span8
    :&markdown
      To install Fuse MQ 
  
      * [download](../download.html) the Fuse MQ distro 
      * [checkout](../../source.html) and [build](../../building.html) the Fabric distro locally and untar the mq/fuse-mq tarball
  

.row-fluid
  .span4
    :markdown
      ## Start Fuse MQ
  .span8
    :&markdown
      To start Fuse MQ use the following commands from a shell 

    pre
      | bin/fusemq           (for Unix systems)
      | bin\fusemq.bat       (for Windows systems)    
    
    :&markdown
      Fuse MQ will present itself on the console as shown below
    pre
      | fuse-mq-#{project_version}$ bin/fusemq 
      |
      | FuseMQ:admin@root> 



